metadata.name: Lobster
metadata.description:
She is a brave female warrior of the sea.

A battle is going on wherever she heads across her wild waves.

There is no defeat in her determined heart. Her armor is light but very sturdy, and she cannot pierce any weapon.

Her blood, burning red, is ruled by her cold spirit. With soberness, and her dedication to her victory, she will eventually become a hero.

Done in Adobe Photoshop CS3
By: YAM
Categories: Original Art, Vivid Code
Resolution: 3000 x 4000

April- 2022
